than you do about anything real!

973
00:39:44.908 --> 00:39:46.542
-That's not true.
-Enjoy your.

974
00:39:46.576 --> 00:39:48.670
-your <i>Golden Girls</i> weekend.
<i>-Golden Girls.</i> wow?

